T02TD1532E:92b-1: shr'i tsakra samba ra sto tra /
T02TD1532E:92b-3: dpal 'khor lo sngom pa la bstod pa /
T02TD1532E:92b-4: bcom ldan 'das 'khor lo sngom pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:92b-5: kun rtog spros bral dri ma rnam dag cing //
T02TD1532E:92b-6: mtsho ltar bde ba chen por ro gcig pa //
T02TD1532E:92b-7: nam mkha'i ngang du sprin dkar dag pa bzhin //
T02TD1532E:92b-8: rang bzhin rnam dag chos rnams mngon gyur te //
T02TD1532E:92b-9: ji ltar mkha' la 'ja' tshon shar ba bzhin //
T02TD1532E:92b-10: gnyis med bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
T02TD1532E:92b-11: yid bzhin nor bu rtog med ji bzhin du //
T02TD1532E:92b-12: gdul bya mchog la sprul sku khro bo'i tshul //
T02TD1532E:92b-13: dpa' bo 'jigs byed gar dgu'i nyams dang ldan //
T02TD1532E:92b-14: sku yi rang bzhin mtshan dang dpe byad ni //
T02TD1532E:92b-15: sgeg dang dpa' dang 'jigs su rung ba'i tshul //
T02TD1532E:92b-16: gsung gi rang bzhin yan lag drug cu ni //
T02TD1532E:92b-17: bzhad dang gshe dang rngam pa'i tshul du bstan //
T02TD1532E:92b-18: thugs kyi rang bzhin gzugs dang ting nge 'dzin //
T02TD1532E:92b-19: zhib sems dpa' rmad du byung ba'i tshul //
T02TD1532E:92b-20: dbang phyug chen po'i sgeg pa'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:92b-21: gnyis med yum la 'khyud nas 'gying bag bzhugs //
T02TD1532E:92b-22: gzhon nu gdong drug dpa' ba'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-0: 'jigs byed dus mtshan g-yas brgyang zhabs kyis @93a * //
T02TD1532E:93a-2: khyab 'jug zhal gsum 'jigs pa'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-3: zhal bzhi mnga' zhing bcu gnyis phyag dang ldan //
T02TD1532E:93a-4: lha chen tshangs pa rgod pa'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-5: g-yas pa ser po bzhed pa'i tshul du bstan //
T02TD1532E:93a-6: tshogs kyi bdag po'i gshe ba'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-7: glang chen pags pas rgyan byas mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1532E:93a-8: sgra gcan lha min nyi zla khar bcug nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-9: rngam pa'i nyams bcom tshangs pa'i mgo bo bsnams //
T02TD1532E:93a-10: brgya byin spyan mangs zhi ba'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-11: sku la spyan gsum gzi brjid ldan pa po //
T02TD1532E:93a-12: me lha tshangs pa zhi ba'i nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-13: thal ba'i tshom bus sku la brgyan pa po //
T02TD1532E:93a-14: klu chen se sha rmad byung nyams bcom nas //
T02TD1532E:93a-15: mi mgo lnga bcu gcig gis do shal byas //
T02TD1532E:93a-16: sku gsung thugs la sdug bsngal gsum nub pas //
T02TD1532E:93a-17: thams cad bde ba chen por thugs su chud //
T02TD1532E:93a-18: yang dag ting 'dzin rang bzhin bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1532E:93a-19: 'khor lo'i dbus na g-yas brkyang sbyor bas bzhugs //
T02TD1532E:93a-20: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog mthing gar bstan //
T02TD1532E:93a-21: thabs kyi tshul gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
T02TD1532E:93a-22: thugs rje mchog gyur de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93a-23: de yi yum gyur rdo rje phag mo ni ;
T02TD1532E:93a-24: / sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma //
T02TD1532E:93a-25: bdud bzhi bcom nas bde chen thugs chud ma //
T02TD1532E:93a-26: gnyis med yum gyur de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93a-27: zhi sogs las mdzad ye shes bzhi yi sku //
T02TD1532E:93a-28: tshad med bzhi dang phyag rgya bzhi ldan ma //
T02TD1532E:93a-29: phyogs bzhi padma'i dbus na bzhugs pa yi //
T02TD1532E:93a-30: mkha' 'gro yum bzhi mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93a-31: rtag pa la sogs de bzhin gshegs pa bzhi //
T02TD1532E:93a-32: bum pa bzhi dang bdud rtsis bkang ba'i snod //
T02TD1532E:93a-33: mtshams bzhir mchod pa'i gzugs kyis gnas pa yi //
T02TD1532E:93a-34: thabs shes dbyer med de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93a-35: sems ni skye ba med par thugs chung cing //
T02TD1532E:93a-36: mi bskyod rigs su sku mdog mthing gar bstan //
T02TD1532E:93a-37: rnam thar brgyad rtsibs thugs rtags rdo rjes brgyan //
T02TD1532E:93a-38: mkha' spyod yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93a-39: gsung ni sgra brnyan lta bur thugs chud cing //
T02TD1532E:93b-0: 'od dpag med rigs sku @93b mdog dmar por bstan //
T02TD1532E:93b-1: rnam thar brgyad rtsibs gsung rtags padmas brgyan //
T02TD1532E:93b-2: sa spyod yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93b-3: sku ni sgyu ma lta bur thugs chud cing //
T02TD1532E:93b-4: rnam dag rigs su sku mdog dkar por bstan //
T02TD1532E:93b-5: rnam thar brgyad rtsibs sku rtags 'khor los brgyan //
T02TD1532E:93b-6: sa 'og yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93b-7: gshin rje brtan sogs khro mo chen mo brgyad //
T02TD1532E:93b-8: mi 'am ci sogs gdul phyir tha dad bzhugs //
T02TD1532E:93b-9: khva gdong la sogs lha mo brgyad po rnams //
T02TD1532E:93b-10: dam tshig 'khor lor bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93b-11: rin chen las grub dpag med gzhal yas khang //
T02TD1532E:93b-12: byang chub mchog gi chos rnams yongs rdzogs pa //
T02TD1532E:93b-13: gtso bo bde chen thugs kyi snang ba ni //
T02TD1532E:93b-14: sna tshogs rgyan dang lha mo'i tshogs kyis mdzes //
T02TD1532E:93b-15: chos rnams tshad med dur khrod brgyad kyis bskor //
T02TD1532E:93b-16: rnam par gzigs shing tha dad gdong du bstan //
T02TD1532E:93b-17: nyan thos rang rgyal 'khor los sgyur sogs brgyad //
T02TD1532E:93b-18: phyogs rnams skyong zhing klu dang srin po'i gzugs //
T02TD1532E:93b-19: thugs rjes nyon mongs bsreg mdzad 'bar ba'i phreng //
T02TD1532E:93b-20: rnam snang rang bzhin thar pa'i grong khyer mchog / bde chen bzhugs gnas de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1532E:93b-21: bcom ldan 'das dpal 'khor lo sdom pa la bstod pa kha che'i pandi ta chen po bram ze rin chen rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1532E:93b-23: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po pandi ta ma h'a dzny'a na dad bod kyi lo ts'a ba mar pa chos kyi dbang phyug gis bsgyur ba'o//
